# Twiga Scan Environment Configuration Template
# Copy this file to .env and update with your values

# ===========================================
# CRITICAL: .env File Setup Instructions
# ===========================================
# Due to Pydantic Settings behavior, list values (CORS_ORIGINS, ALLOWED_FILE_TYPES)
# cannot be set via .env file. They must be configured via environment variables
# or by modifying config.py directly.
#
# For production deployment:
# 1. Copy this file: cp env.example .env
# 2. Update the values below
# 3. Set CORS_ORIGINS via environment variable:
#    export CORS_ORIGINS='["https://yourdomain.com","https://api.yourdomain.com"]'
#
# OR modify config.py defaults directly for your deployment.
# ===========================================

